snippet.title: Gravity Garden - alpha 6 gameplay
snippet.description:
Two minutes of gameplay from the next build of Gravity Garden. New stylized shaders for a cartoon-ish look.  New harvesting mechanics and seed inventory. Shinier, floaty ribbon things. []-)

More info and early access:
https://don-whitaker.itch.io/gravity-garden

Gravity Garden Developer Diary Playlist:
https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLe3HrZjzh8d-d26qKKp7636ngwF1bYC0S

Music from Jukedeck - create your own at http://jukedeck.com
